 503        private bool ParseHotkey(string hotkey, out uint modifiers, out uint key)
 0504        {
 0505            modifiers = 0;

 507
 0508            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(hotkey))

 0512            foreach (string part in parts)
 0513            {
 0514                string lowerPart = part.Trim().ToLower();
 0515                switch (lowerPart)
 516                {
 517                    case "ctrl":
 0518                        modifiers |= 2;

 520                    case "alt":

 0525                        break;
 526                    default:
 0527                        if (lowerPart.Length > 0)
 0528                        {
 0529                            key = (uint)Char.ToUpper(lowerPart[0]);
 0530                        }
 0531                        break;
 532                }

 1027        private void DataGridView_CellFormatting(object sender, DataGridViewCellFormattingEventArgs e)
 01028        {
 01029            if (e.Value == null || e.RowIndex < 0 || e.ColumnIndex < 0)
 01030                return;
 1031
 01032            var dgv = sender as DataGridView;
 01033            var cell = dgv[e.ColumnIndex, e.RowIndex];
 01034            if (cell == null) return;
 1035
 1036            // 仅在单元格可见时执行格式化
 01037            if (!dgv.Rows[e.RowIndex].Displayed || !dgv.Columns[e.ColumnIndex].Visible)
 01038                return;
 1039
 1040            // 保存原始字体和最小字体大小
 01041            Font originalFont = cell.Style.Font ?? dgv.DefaultCellStyle.Font ?? SystemFonts.DefaultFont;
 01042            float minFontSize = 6f;
 01043            float currentFontSize = originalFont.Size;
 01044            string text = e.Value.ToString();
 1045
 1046            // 获取单元格内容区域宽度
 01047            int cellWidth = dgv.Columns[e.ColumnIndex].Width - 10; // 减去内边距
 01048            if (cellWidth <= 0) return;
 1049
 1050            // 快速检查文本长度，避免不必要的字体调整
 01051            if (text.Length <= 10) // 短文本通常不需要调整字体
 01052            {
 1053                // 恢复默认字体（如果之前有调整）
 01054                if (cell.Style.Font != null && cell.Style.Font.Size != originalFont.Size)
 01055                {
 01056                    cell.Style.Font = originalFont;
 01057                }
 01058            }
 1059            else
 01060            {
 1061                // 创建临时Graphics对象用于测量文本
 01062                using Graphics g = dgv.CreateGraphics();
 1063
 1064                // 测量当前字体下文本宽度
 01065                SizeF textSize = g.MeasureString(text, originalFont);
 1066
 1067                // 如果文本宽度超过单元格宽度，逐步缩小字体
 01068                if (textSize.Width > cellWidth)
 01069                {
 1070                    // 计算需要缩小的大致比例
 01071                    float scaleFactor = cellWidth / textSize.Width;
 01072                    currentFontSize = Math.Max(minFontSize, originalFont.Size * scaleFactor);
 1073
 1074                    // 设置最终字体
 01075                    cell.Style.Font = new Font(originalFont.FontFamily, currentFontSize, originalFont.Style);
 01076                }
 1077                else
 01078                {
 1079                    // 恢复默认字体
 01080                    if (cell.Style.Font != null && cell.Style.Font.Size != originalFont.Size)
 01081                    {
 01082                        cell.Style.Font = originalFont;
 01083                    }
 01084                }
 01085            }
 1086
 1087            // 设置匹配行高亮颜色
 01088            if (dgv.Rows[e.RowIndex].DataBoundItem is DataRowView dataRowView && _matchedRows.Contains(dataRowView.Row))
 01089            {
 01090                e.CellStyle.BackColor = Color.FromArgb(255, 192, 0); // 橙色R255,G192,B0
 01091            }
 01092        }

 1863        // 实现Windows资源管理器风格的自然排序比较器
 1864        private class NaturalSortComparer : IComparer<string>
 1865        {
 1866            // 改进的正则表达式，支持浮点数
 01867            private static readonly Regex _regex = new Regex(@"(\d+\.\d+|\d+)");
 1868
 1869            public int Compare(string x, string y)
 01870            {
 01871                if (x == null && y == null)
 01872                    return 0;
 01873                if (x == null)
 01874                    return -1;
 01875                if (y == null)
 01876                    return 1;
 1877
 1878                // 分割字符串和数字（包括浮点数）
 01879                var xParts = _regex.Split(x);
 01880                var yParts = _regex.Split(y);
 1881
 01882                int minLength = Math.Min(xParts.Length, yParts.Length);
 01883                for (int i = 0; i < minLength; i++)
 01884                {
 1885                    // 比较当前部分
 01886                    if (i % 2 == 0) // 非数字部分
 01887                    {
 1888                        // 使用与Windows资源管理器一致的不区分大小写比较
 01889                        int result = string.Compare(xParts[i], yParts[i], StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase);
 01890                        if (result != 0)
 01891                            return result;
 01892                    }
 1893                    else // 数字部分（可能是整数或浮点数）
 01894                    {
 1895                        // 尝试解析为浮点数
 01896                        if (double.TryParse(xParts[i], out double xNum) && double.TryParse(yParts[i], out double yNum))
 01897                        {
 01898                            int result = xNum.CompareTo(yNum);
 01899                            if (result != 0)
 01900                                return result;
 01901                        }
 1902                        else
 01903                        {
 1904                            // 如果不能解析为数字，则按字符串比较
 01905                            int result = string.Compare(xParts[i], yParts[i], StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase)
 01906                            if (result != 0)
 01907                                return result;
 01908                        }
 01909                    }
 01910                }
 1911
 1912                // 如果前面的部分都相同，则比较长度
 01913                return xParts.Length.CompareTo(yParts.Length);
 01914            }
 1915        }
